# 2026.04.22.0

- **Full rewrite** — EtherCalc now runs on the Cloudflare Workers
  fullstack (Hono + Durable Objects + D1 + KV + R2), backed by
  Miniflare locally. The legacy Node + Redis + socket.io 0.9 stack is
  retired.
- **Automatic legacy migration** — existing grains carry their full
  spreadsheet history forward. On first boot, `run_grain.sh` detects
  `/var/dump/` (per-key text files) or `/var/dump.json` (single-blob)
  and streams it into the new Durable Object layer. A `/var/.migrated`
  sentinel prevents re-runs.
- **All prior features preserved** — multi-sheet routing at `/=:room`,
  REST API, XLSX/ODS/CSV export, real-time collaboration.

